3B. Saijah: The Psychic Migraine (If Orion Goes Before Saijah)
Context: Identical setup—Saijah is dealing with the Eldergleam migraine. But Varon has already delivered his message to Orion.
The Arrival: Varon (Clan Recognition)
Read Aloud: "You're staring toward the southeast horizon when you hear footsteps in the snow behind you. You turn to see Varon approaching—the surgically modified Bosmer from your shadowscale satellite clan, hiding as a Breton among the Stormcloaks. You recognized each other through clan signs and Jel, but you've never actually spoken beyond that brief acknowledgment.
'Saijah,' he says quietly, stopping beside you. 'Vena. Forgive me—I just finished speaking with Orion. Brotherhood matters.'
