PART IV: THE COUNCIL OF WAR (THE THREE FIRES)
Setting
The Stormcloaks are either packing to leave (Scenario A/C) or have already left (Scenario B/D). The party is alone with Bjorn at the campfire.
Throughout the session, the party has encountered:
