The Heat Sink: While others shiver in the Pale's winds, Davinia stands in light robes. Snow lands on her shoulders and fails to melt.
The Voice of Command: When she speaks to crowds or gives orders, her voice carries an ancient, echoing resonance that makes mortals instinctively want to bow their heads.
